| !Setup file for ZapSpell

Set ZapSpell$Dir <Obey$Dir>
Set ZapSpell$Path <ZapSpell$Dir>.<Zap$Country>.,<ZapSpell$Dir>.UK.,<ZapSpell$Dir>.
Set ZapSpell$Menus ZapSpell:Menus
Set ZapSpell$Templates ZapSpell:Templates
Set ZapSpell$Scripts ZapSpell:Scripts
Set ZapSpell$Sprites ZapSpell:Sprites
Set ZapSpellDictionary$Path ZapUser:ZapSpell.Dictionary.,ZapSpell$Dir.Dictionary.
|Set ZapSpell$Command (IMPRESSIONSPELL_LOADDIC "ZapSpellDictionary:DefaultDic")
IconSprites <ZapSpell$Dir>.Filetypes

| The following has been split into two paths to avoid buffer overflow - the paths are very full
Set ZapSpellCCShared$Path System:!CCShared.,<CCShared$Dir>.
| The 'ImpressionSpell' module should be called "!SpellMod", somewhere on the path:
Set ZapSpellImpression$Path <ZapSpell$Dir>.Modules.,ZapSpellCCShared:RMStore.,Impression:RMStore.,<Impression$Dir>.RMStore.,<ImpressionPublisher$Resources>.RMStore.,<ImpressionStyle$Resources>.RMStore.,<Junior$Dir>.RMStore.,Junior:RMStore.
